Hou

23:18.660 --> 23:20.620
Houj

23:20.620 --> 23:22.580
Houjou

23:22.580 --> 23:24.540
Houjou Su

23:24.540 --> 23:28.300
Houjou Suzu

23:26.880 --> 23:34.640
Tell me, what is our address?
And the house number?

23:35.450 --> 23:36.950
Kure
Upper Naganoki
House 808

23:35.950 --> 23:36.820
I see it!

23:36.950 --> 23:37.880
We're going.

23:38.750 --> 23:39.970
Have a good trip.

23:41.310 --> 23:45.550
It seems that everyone here has work connected with the fleet.

23:55.710 --> 23:57.200
Ms. Hojo.

24:00.680 --> 24:02.110
Ms. Hojo.

